{"parentUuid":"089cfd79-230a-40d3-846c-f8d4f0df738a","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01NYBDQ3TmuZ2A6yGBHgtN8x","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ユーザーがVSCodeが日本語設定になっているため、メニューや設定が分かりにくいとおっしゃっています。\n\nこれは一般的な話で、ユーザーが英語設定に変更したいのかもしれません。\n\nVSCodeの言語設定を英語に変更する方法：\n1. Command Paletteで「Configure Display Language」を検索\n2. または、拡張機能「Japanese Language Pack」をアンインストール\n3. または、settings.jsonで `\"locale\": \"en\"` を設定\n\nユーザーの意思表示としては「日本語は分かりにくい」ということなので、英語に変更する方法を提案するのが良いでしょう。\n\n簡潔に、実践的な方法を2-3つ提案します。","signature":""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":262,"cache_read_input_tokens":44919,"output_tokens":483,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":262,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":10,"output_tokens":483,"cache_read_input_tokens":44919,"cache_creation_input_tokens":262,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":262},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaqrZd1FMXYeQyYbfdcJo","type":"assistant","uuid":"d2c219da-0b12-4e68-aa00-c5a9bbdba9fa","timestamp":"2026-05-08T22:01:37.128Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/home/makoto1234/makoto_projects","sessionId":"98dd362e-6cc4-4e23-bc7a-c67c3f0df89e","version":"2.1.136","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"d2c219da-0b12-4e68-aa00-c5a9bbdba9fa","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01NYBDQ3TmuZ2A6yGBHgtN8x","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"VSCodeを英語に変更する方法：\n\n**方法1: 拡張機能をアンインストール（最も簡単）**\n1. VSCodeの拡張パネル（左サイドバー）を開く\n2. 「Japanese Language Pack for Visual Studio Code」を検索\n3. アンインストール → VSCode再起動\n\n**方法2: settings.jsonで直接指定**\n1. `Ctrl+Shift+P` → 「Preferences: Open User Settings (JSON)」\n2. 以下を追加：\n   ```json\n   \"locale\": \"en\"\n   ```\n3. VSCode再起動\n\n**方法3: Command Paletteで変更**\n1. `Ctrl+Shift+P` → 「Configure Display Language」と入力\n2. 「English」を選択 → 再起動\n\nこれでメニューやCommand Paletteが英語になり、検索時も分かりやすくなります。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":262,"cache_read_input_tokens":44919,"output_tokens":483,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":262,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":10,"output_tokens":483,"cache_read_input_tokens":44919,"cache_creation_input_tokens":262,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":262},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaqrZd1FMXYeQyYbfdcJo","type":"assistant","uuid":"df65cc4c-9fe9-4b7f-88a9-b6e0b8b12ea3","timestamp":"2026-05-08T22:01:38.874Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/home/makoto1234/makoto_projects","sessionId":"98dd362e-6cc4-4e23-bc7a-c67c3f0df89e","version":"2.1.136","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
